\n9 Mid-term Presentations\n科技演說與簡報演練\n10 Visual Aids\n科技演說與簡報:製作有效圖表及投影片\n11 Visual Aids\n科技演說與簡報:如何解說有效圖表及投影片\n12 科技職場文化業師分享會：\nSpeaker: Joseph Chan, Product Manager,\nMeitu (美圖）Inc.\n13 Cross-culture communication in Tech world\n科技職場跨文化接待演練\n14 Explaining Experiments and Results\n科技演說與簡報：實驗結果撰寫與解說\n15 Explaining Experiments and Results\n科技演說與簡報：實驗結果撰寫與解說\n16 Impact Techniques\n科技演說與簡報：技巧加強\n17 Final Presentations\n期末報告發表\n18 期末報告發表“", "en": "“1 Introduction\n2 Presentation Openings\n3 Vocal Delivery＆ Body Language\n4 Speech Organization\n5 Speech Organization: Focus on Product features\n6 How to Simplify the Language\n7 Presentation Closing\n8 Mid-term Presentations\n9 Mid-term Presentations\n10 Visual Aids\n11 Visual Aids\n12 Speaker: Joseph Chan, Product Manager,\nMeitu (美圖）Inc.\n13 Cross-culture communication in Tech world\n14 Explaining Experiments and Results\n15 Explaining Experiments and Results\n16 Impact Techniques\n17 Final Presentations\n18 Final Presentations“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "TBA", "en": "TBA"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "“1. 出席 10％\n2. 課堂參與 15％\n3. 小考和作業 25％\n4. 演講與簡報 30％\n5. 專題呈現 20％“", "en": "“1. Attendance 10％\n2. Participation 15％\n3. Quizzes and assignments 25％\n4. Speeches and presentations 30％\n5. Final course project 20％“"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "By appointment", "en": "By appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "應用英文", "en": "應用英文"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言溝通", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "文化視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量"]}, {"competencies": "自主學習", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "學習檔案評量"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Language & Communication Skills", "rating": "(5)VeryHi